node.text: Do you remember when you could just go anywhere you wanted? Hop on a plane, into a car or onto a scooter and away you go! 8 weeks into another lockdown and I'm craving an adventure!!! This was the first time I went to Barracuda Lake. @liquidlifeindo took us there and took this shot. Where is the first place you'll go once we can all travel freely again? #travel #freediving #philippines #underwater #cliffs

node.text: Starting next week I am going to be posting our vlogs to Facebook! We're going to start by re-editing some of our older videos and then once we get some momentum going we'll be posting Facebook versions of our YT videos at the same time! Its been heaps of fun watching the old videos again. Thanks @cb_free87 for taking this photo and thanks @dodirecoder for all your work editing! #freedivingvlog #ocean #underwater #diving

node.text: Who's keen for me to run some surf apnea/surf survival training? This is one of our courses at @liquidlifeindo for the past few years my partner Shane and I have had a dedicated surf apnea centre in Bali so until I can get back over there it would be great to teach some of those lessons in Australia! #surfsurvival #training #australia #pooltraining

node.text: Before I got home from Exmouth we had the chance to dive with this amazing loggerhead turtle. He was between 50 and 80 years old. It felt like diving with a dinosaur! @brinkleydavies in this shot. #freediving #australia #westernaustralia #turtle

node.text:
I've been getting a lot of questions about why I'm not competing at Vertical Blue this year and the answer is simple...we're still not allowed to leave Australia 😂 It's been amazing watching everyone doing monster dives though! 

We have been having a magical time at the farm. We're getting ready for baby Ari, planting birthday trees and landscaping. With the help of @drawn_2water we have even built a tiny house! 

I feel like this will be a time in our lives that we always look back on. When we lived in a little house we built on the farm and the kids were young 😊 #farmlife #australia #paradise

node.text: This was the most intense adventure I've ever been on and I turned around right at the beginning 😂 head to the link in my bio to watch the whole thing! @seumascj @cb_free87 @dave_deniro @reuben.demunck what a time! Lets never do it again 😂 #cavediving #australia #adventure #freediving

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Adam Stern on July 08, 2021 tagging @adventurefreedivers. May be an image of nature and body of water.

node.text: Where was this photo/video taken? Its a place where you can come up out of the water and eat blackberries! You get 3 guesses and every correct answer goes in the draw to win a Freediving Family hoodie towel posted anywhere in the world. Freediver @adventurefreedivers #freediving #underwater #blackberries #mystery #australia

node.text: The first video from our trip to Ningaloo Reef is up! It is such a nuts place. Everything and anything can just pop up out of the distance in the water. I've never been somewhere with so much life and so many possibilities. The diver here is @seumascj #freediving #australia #ningaloo #westernaustralia #ocean #nature
